[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    799[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mLocation:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m "Why These Services" Amazon SageMaker description; existing TODO acknowledging the model-promotion gap.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    800[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mProblem:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Same chapter-wide pattern, sharper here because the model count is materially larger (10-30 treatment-comparator pairs × 3 model families = 30-90 model artifacts per portfolio refresh cycle). The 4.7 review's Finding A5 named the same gap with 15 artifacts; here the multiple is 2-6x.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    801[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    802[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106mTreatment-response-specific reasons:[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    803[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    804[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106m1[38;2;191;97;106m.[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mThe promotion path's clinical-validation suite is more demanding.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m The 4.7 promotion required cohort-calibration parity. The 4.8 promotion requires cohort-calibration parity, propensity-overlap re-verification, sensitivity-analysis re-execution, and cross-method-family agreement. The promotion gate is multi-test, and the test ordering and gating logic is non-trivial.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    805[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    806[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106m2[38;2;191;97;106m.[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mModel retirement and supersession are first-class.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Some models will, over time, lose calibration faster than retraining can recover, become structurally biased in ways that fairness instrumentation cannot fully correct, or be superseded by a regulatory-cleared alternative. The catalog needs an explicit sunset path: a treatment-comparator pair can be retired from production with explicit rationale, and the retirement triggers downstream cleanup. The Honest Take's "models that quietly degrade in production because nobody is responsible for retiring them" framing is the right operational concern; the architecture should encode the retirement primitive explicitly.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    807[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
